2012-11-18  gpFinder 2.0
	* Bugfixes

2012-11-18  gpFinder 2.0rc3
	* Enable more features in net-mounted ftp volumes (copy, paste...)
	* Unique icon for netmount
	* Show all icons in toolbar by default
	* Fix ftp_size usage
	* Fix quicklook
	* Selecting next/previous will wrap

2012-11-11  gpFinder 2.0rc2
	* Tar & Zip archive without exec()
	* Ftp without MLST
	* netmount returns open information instead of prompting sync
	* Don't check for subdirs in stat() functions
	* Using getScandir() instead of _scandir()
	* Using $volume->separator exlusively instead of DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR

2012-11-02  gpFinder 2.0rc1
	* Added saveData and returnData configuration options
	* Added MountVolume() method
	* File inclusion handled by Finder.class.php
	* Removed FinderConnector
	* Using constants for chmod settings
	* Check tmbPath works for mixed OSes
	* Removed beeper
	* use call_user_func() for callbacks
	* Added *-before events

